@node MAIN "iconbox_plugin: Introduction"


    @{b}iconbox_plugin@{ub}

        by @{b}Ali Graham@{ub} <agraham@hal9000.net.au>



    @{b}iconbox_plugin@{ub} is a PLUGIN that offers a
    space to render icon images in EasyGUI applications.
    It also accepts icons being dropped onto it; this
    requires that the window be declared as an AppWindow
    in the EasyGUI declaration.

    ------------------------------------------------------------

